title: Qualcomm enters server CPU market with 24-core ARM chip - ITworld
text:
There are 1 comment on the ITworld story from Friday, titled Qualcomm enters server CPU market with 24-core ARM chip . In it, ITworld reports that:
Qualcomm has revealed its plans to enter the server CPU market with a custom processor based on a design from U.K. chip company ARM. Qualcomm becomes the latest vendor to build a server chip using the ARM architecture, which is widely used in smartphones and tablets.
Join the discussion below, or Read more at ITworld.
